      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SCHEDULED之后应该有个SEND_REQUESTED状态，表示已请求发送但还没确认成功。从那里分叉：成功就到SENT，失败就是FAIL_TO_SEND。失败的数据要回流到PatientRecords做人工复核。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "SEND_REQUESTED",
        "SENT",
        "FAIL_TO_SEND",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：LabAnalyzer → PENDING → SCHEDULED → SEND_REQUESTED，然后SEND_REQUESTED分两支到SENT和FAIL_TO_SEND，FAIL_TO_SEND指向PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "PENDING",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "SEND_REQUESTED",
        "SENT",
        "FAIL_TO_SEND",
