      "utterance": "确认一下：PENDING → UNPROCESSABLE是一条独立分支；SCHEDULED除了正常流转，还能到DELETED，然后DELETED进HIPAA_Vault。UNPROCESSABLE的数据也需要进HIPAA_Vault归档吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
